msgstr "GlobalPayments WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: globalpayments-gateway-provider-for-woocommerce.php
msgid "https://github.com/globalpayments/globalpayments-woocommerce"
msgstr "https://github.com/globalpayments/globalpayments-woocommerce"

#. Description of the plugin
#: globalpayments-gateway-provider-for-woocommerce.php
msgid "This extension allows WooCommerce to use the available Global Payments payment gateways. All card data is tokenized using the respective gateway's tokenization service."
msgstr "此擴充功能允許 WooCommerce 使用 Global Payments 提供的支付網關。所有卡片資料都將透過相應網關的代碼化服務進行代碼化處理。"

